dc_title_s: Map of the Pacific coast near Huatulco, Mexico; Map of the Pacific coast near Salinas and Tehuantepec, Mexico; Map of the Pacific coast of Santa Rosa Department, Guatemala, and Sonsonate Department, El Salvador
